24:56.516 --> 24:58.429
I'm not pleased at all about that.

24:58.429 --> 25:01.363
- Would you be so kind just to
leave me here with the owners

25:01.363 --> 25:02.248
for two minutes, please?

25:02.248 --> 25:03.448
I appreciate your
feedback, thank you guys.

25:03.448 --> 25:06.141
- [Guests] Thank you very much.

25:07.238 --> 25:08.215
- [Gordon] Jesus.

25:08.215 --> 25:09.084
- [T.J.] I'm sorry.

25:09.084 --> 25:12.907
- [Gordon] No, no, story
of my fucking life.

25:14.033 --> 25:16.419
- You asked me here to come and help you

25:16.419 --> 25:18.916
but you both need to change your ways.

25:18.916 --> 25:21.886
You won't open up to me and you
won't open up to each other.

25:21.886 --> 25:24.039
Your business is literally
dying because you won't

25:24.039 --> 25:27.155
communicate, it's like you don't care.

25:27.155 --> 25:29.520
I can't even start to move
forward because I'm not

25:29.520 --> 25:32.316
feeling the fucking, the hunger

25:32.316 --> 25:34.431
that both of you want this place to work.

25:34.431 --> 25:37.559
So I'm just saying fuck it, sell it.

25:39.803 --> 25:41.628
I'm going downstairs.

25:42.551 --> 25:43.941
Not again, fuck.

25:47.128 --> 25:49.648
(door slams)

25:52.850 --> 25:57.282
- Oh my gosh, Gordon can't
even find the solution.

25:59.592 --> 26:03.416
It takes two, it takes
two hands to get out.

26:04.406 --> 26:05.274
- I love this place,

26:05.274 --> 26:06.816
I love this place with all my heart

26:06.816 --> 26:08.910
but the way things are going

26:08.910 --> 26:12.473
the revelation is it's just not worth it.

26:13.533 --> 26:15.965
- I'm really struggling to
get through to Chris and T.J.

26:15.965 --> 26:17.277
The person who knows
them better than anyone

26:17.277 --> 26:19.192
is their mother Trudy.

26:19.192 --> 26:22.130
I'm hoping she may help
me to unlock that divide

26:22.130 --> 26:26.908
between them and hopefully
get these two back on track.

26:31.305 --> 26:32.722
Hello, I came to see you this morning

26:32.722 --> 26:34.538
'cause I need your help.

26:34.538 --> 26:36.615
I'm struggling to get through to T.J.

26:36.615 --> 26:39.914
and I'm struggling to
get through to Chris.

26:39.914 --> 26:41.041
They don't communicate,

26:41.041 --> 26:43.213
they don't drive the business forward,

26:43.213 --> 26:44.974
they just bicker and butt heads.

26:44.974 --> 26:46.017
Why is that?

26:47.289 --> 26:50.751
- I don't know, I don't know why.

26:50.751 --> 26:52.678
- How much does that inn mean to you?

26:52.678 --> 26:56.244
I mean, what does it
stand for in your family?

26:56.244 --> 26:58.880
- It stands for the home
work, if nothing else.

26:58.880 --> 27:00.049
- Yeah.

27:00.049 --> 27:03.048
- We all had to work in there.

27:03.048 --> 27:07.456
- You should be reaping the
rewards of the family success

27:07.456 --> 27:09.455
and nearly six decades.

27:10.393 --> 27:12.692
But how would it make
you feel if this business

27:12.692 --> 27:14.604
was sold to a different family now?

27:14.604 --> 27:19.231
I mean all that work of you
and your husband's commitment.

27:19.231 --> 27:22.794
- I don't want another bitter change yet.

27:25.212 --> 27:29.821
I really don't want to see it
go down the street tomorrow.

27:29.821 --> 27:32.550
I wanna see those two
can't come back together

27:32.550 --> 27:35.157
and get it back on their feet.

27:36.211 --> 27:38.757
- I really want to help your family,

27:38.757 --> 27:41.093
and I really want to
keep this business alive

27:41.093 --> 27:42.391
for another 60 years.

27:42.391 --> 27:45.455
So we're gonna have to get
them to talk to each other.

27:45.455 --> 27:48.007
Otherwise the business is doomed.

27:48.007 --> 27:50.404
- Well, you're right.

27:50.404 --> 27:54.294
- I'm gonna need your help, please.

27:54.294 --> 27:55.955
- You got it.

27:55.955 --> 27:58.582
- Thank you, I'll see you back at the inn.

27:58.582 --> 27:59.451
- Okay.

27:59.451 --> 28:02.058
- Okay, thank you my darling.

28:03.171 --> 28:04.440
- Coming up.

28:04.440 --> 28:05.966
- And the two of you to
be able to communicate

28:05.966 --> 28:08.934
as brother and sister
is more important than

28:08.934 --> 28:09.803
even this inn.

28:09.803 --> 28:14.756
- [Gordon] Has change come
too late for the Curtis House?

28:19.297 --> 28:21.067
- [Gordon] The Curtis House
in Woodbury, Connecticut

28:21.067 --> 28:24.961
is sinking because the two
owners won't speak to each other.

28:24.961 --> 28:26.970
And despite the hotel's dire situation

28:26.970 --> 28:29.948
I've been unable to get
through to Chris and T.J.

28:29.948 --> 28:32.500
C'mon Chris, you don't care.

28:32.500 --> 28:35.835
So I went to see their
mum, and I need your help.

28:35.835 --> 28:37.156
- You got it.

28:37.156 --> 28:39.908
- Now, Trudy has organised
a family intervention

28:39.908 --> 28:41.915
to let T.J. and Chris know
how much their fighting

28:41.915 --> 28:44.608
is hurting the inn and
everyone around them.

28:44.608 --> 28:45.477
Hi guys.

28:45.477 --> 28:46.346
- Hi Gordon.

28:46.346 --> 28:49.286
- First of all to you guys,
I appreciate you being here.

28:49.286 --> 28:53.192
Your mum has brought everyone
together just to talk to you

28:53.192 --> 28:56.034
from the bottom of their hearts.

28:56.034 --> 28:58.716
I hope this is gonna open
your eyes because right now

28:58.716 --> 29:00.123
I don't know what will.

29:00.123 --> 29:01.840
Who'd like to go first?

29:01.840 --> 29:04.561
Tess, what have you got to say my darling?

29:04.561 --> 29:07.570
- Mom, I think that you're
spread way too thin.

29:07.570 --> 29:09.065
When you think that the mounting work

29:09.065 --> 29:11.321
is getting to be too much,
you're getting frustrated

29:11.321 --> 29:13.656
and eventually it's bound to spill over.

29:13.656 --> 29:15.576
But I think that for the two of you

29:15.576 --> 29:18.194
to still be able to talk
and communicate as brother

29:18.194 --> 29:22.365
and sister is more important
than even this inn.

29:29.998 --> 29:32.283
- [Gordon] Karen, darling?

29:32.283 --> 29:33.756
- I've sat with both of you,

29:33.756 --> 29:36.726
many times talked about all the problems,

29:36.726 --> 29:38.852
you guys just go back and forth.

29:38.852 --> 29:41.588
There's no resolve, nothing.

29:41.588 --> 29:43.340
You have to get on the same page about it,

29:43.340 --> 29:47.502
it's way too much for
everyone in this place.

29:47.502 --> 29:50.997
It's awful, something has to change.

29:50.997 --> 29:52.662
- [Gordon] Thank you darling.

29:52.662 --> 29:53.727
Babe, darling?

29:53.727 --> 29:55.215
- Okay, T.J. and Chris

29:55.215 --> 29:58.550
I really hope we can all get through this,

29:58.550 --> 30:01.592
I'm getting too emotional, I can't.

30:02.676 --> 30:06.061
- This is so important,
you've been here for 48 years,

30:06.061 --> 30:08.417
you know this place better than anybody.

30:08.417 --> 30:10.366
- The two of you were so
close for so many years,

30:10.366 --> 30:13.043
I know 'cause I was
there and I've seen it.

30:13.043 --> 30:15.193
We used to come to work and do our job

30:15.193 --> 30:18.734
and really enjoy working with each other.

30:18.734 --> 30:22.309
And with both your stubbornness,
you took that all away

30:22.309 --> 30:23.827
since you two stopped speaking,

30:23.827 --> 30:26.558
everything is going downhill.

30:26.558 --> 30:30.916
I want to help you to get back
together like it used to be.

30:30.916 --> 30:33.243
And I know the Curtis
House can be that way again

30:33.243 --> 30:35.676
and only you two can make that happen.

30:35.676 --> 30:38.661
We all wanna be there
for you and help you.

30:38.661 --> 30:41.798
And with a lot of hope and
help and Gordon's expertise

30:41.798 --> 30:44.976
we can get Connecticut's
oldest inn, Curtis House

30:44.976 --> 30:47.322
back to where it should be.

30:48.891 --> 30:51.566
And you two then can be very very proud

30:51.566 --> 30:53.825
of what you accomplished.

30:56.141 --> 30:57.939
- Trudy my darling,

30:57.939 --> 31:00.237
can these two make it work?

31:00.237 --> 31:03.886
- They sure can, they sure can, they have,

31:06.361 --> 31:09.142
and we're behind them 100%.

31:13.221 --> 31:16.175
- They are desperate beyond belief

31:17.463 --> 31:20.331
to help you make this place work.

31:24.018 --> 31:26.190
You both have to step up.

31:28.981 --> 31:31.602
- When he walks through the
door, I have to be the person

31:31.602 --> 31:34.462
that's there for him. That's it.

31:34.462 --> 31:38.723
But I wanted, I want him to be my guy here

31:38.723 --> 31:42.286
and I wanna be the person who he goes to.

31:43.593 --> 31:46.981
- Chris, do you want to make this work?

31:57.744 --> 31:59.570
Chris and T.J.'s family have come together

31:59.570 --> 32:02.444
for a last ditch attempt to
save the Curtis House Inn,

32:02.444 --> 32:04.760
by getting them to talk
to each other again.

32:04.760 --> 32:07.029
Now Chris has to decide
if he'll commit to the inn

32:07.029 --> 32:09.000
or walk away.

32:09.000 --> 32:12.215
Chris, do you want to make this work?

32:17.964 --> 32:19.093
- Absolutely.

32:23.440 --> 32:26.307
(staff clapping)

32:28.738 --> 32:31.880
It just sucks that we've gone this far.

32:31.880 --> 32:34.448
That I must stop being a
jerk especially to my sister.

32:34.448 --> 32:36.322
All right, now I really just
wanna make my mother proud

32:36.322 --> 32:37.346
and my family proud.

32:37.346 --> 32:38.552
It's been a family
establishment all these years

32:38.552 --> 32:41.680
and I have to make them proud again.

32:43.225 --> 32:45.916
- Christopher and I let
everything else get in the middle

32:45.916 --> 32:46.912
of our relationship

32:46.912 --> 32:49.274
but we have to be each other's number one.

32:49.274 --> 32:50.689
You know, family first.

32:50.689 --> 32:51.946
We can do it.

32:51.946 --> 32:54.436
Family united makes a stronger front.

32:54.436 --> 32:55.305
Ready?

32:55.305 --> 32:57.112
- Yes, absolutely.

32:57.112 --> 32:59.828
- It was the first time we
seen that in three years,

32:59.828 --> 33:01.383
it was like we did it.

33:01.383 --> 33:04.250
(staff clapping)

33:06.945 --> 33:08.493
- [Gordon] With Chris and
T.J. ready for change,

33:08.493 --> 33:13.446
my design team has worked all
night to transform the inn.

33:18.521 --> 33:21.936
And now it's time to reveal
the new look to the team.

33:21.936 --> 33:23.316
Welcome to the new Curtis House,

33:23.316 --> 33:25.402
Connecticut's oldest inn

33:26.361 --> 33:28.135
run by an extraordinary family,

33:28.135 --> 33:29.822
providing a warm

33:29.822 --> 33:32.923
and welcoming experience
for other families.

33:32.923 --> 33:33.791
Excited?

33:33.791 --> 33:34.674
- [Babe] I can't wait.

33:34.674 --> 33:35.879
- [Gordon] You're gonna love it.

33:35.879 --> 33:36.790
You ready to go inside?

33:36.790 --> 33:37.734
- Yes we are.

33:37.734 --> 33:40.083
Let's go, follow me, please,

33:40.083 --> 33:41.387
please come in.

33:42.726 --> 33:43.769
- Oh my God.

33:44.914 --> 33:46.217
- Look at this!

33:48.797 --> 33:49.701
- Oh, my God.

33:49.701 --> 33:50.954
- [Babe] That is awesome.

33:50.954 --> 33:53.773
- [Gordon] Welcome to
your amazing new lobby.

33:53.773 --> 33:54.816
The comfort.

33:56.464 --> 34:00.374
- A de-cluttered, very
welcoming, warm space.

34:01.319 --> 34:05.367
Over here we have these
stunning silhouettes,

34:05.367 --> 34:09.623
they are historical
portraits of all your family.

34:12.877 --> 34:16.012
T.J., come here, come over here.

34:16.012 --> 34:16.880
You okay?

34:17.880 --> 34:19.455
Come here.

34:19.455 --> 34:20.973
- The silhouettes of
the family and the staff

34:20.973 --> 34:22.364
it put me over the edge because

34:22.364 --> 34:24.427
this business was built on that.

34:24.427 --> 34:27.405
- [Gordon] You need to
celebrate your family history,

34:27.405 --> 34:29.230
not be trapped by it.

34:30.216 --> 34:32.369
Now one thing that concerned
me on my first arrival

34:32.369 --> 34:35.719
was the check-in and that reservation book

34:35.719 --> 34:38.900
that was gathering all that
sensitive personal data.

34:38.900 --> 34:40.464
Come over, please.

34:41.572 --> 34:43.052
- [Chris] Oh my God, what is that?

34:43.052 --> 34:45.507
- [T.J.] Oh my God, a computer.

34:45.507 --> 34:47.688
- Now we know they didn't
have these in 1754,

34:47.688 --> 34:50.025
but you can, okay.

34:50.025 --> 34:53.726
The credit cards and all the
personal details will be safe.

34:53.726 --> 34:55.940
- We've had that red book for years,

34:55.940 --> 34:58.053
I'm so happy it's gone.

34:58.053 --> 35:00.674
If aunt T.J. brings the red
book back out, I will burn it.

35:00.674 --> 35:03.511
I'll do anything to make sure
we never see that thing again.

35:03.511 --> 35:06.146
- I'd like to take you
upstairs now, to my room.

35:06.146 --> 35:07.015
You ready?

35:07.927 --> 35:08.796
Let's go.

35:10.330 --> 35:12.454
You'll be pleased to know
we've repaired the door handle

35:12.454 --> 35:14.037
so it actually works.

35:14.037 --> 35:15.402
Welcome.

35:15.402 --> 35:16.271
- [Babe] Oh my God.

35:16.271 --> 35:17.488
- [Karen] Wow.

35:19.198 --> 35:21.805
- [Gordon] C'mon, have a look.

35:23.072 --> 35:24.269
- Wow.

35:24.269 --> 35:25.559
Again, steeped in history

35:25.559 --> 35:28.719
but encapsulating that modern elegance.

35:28.719 --> 35:31.159
The panels on the wall, elevate the scope,

35:31.159 --> 35:32.235
the depth of the room.

35:32.235 --> 35:35.884
T.J., Betty the ghost has her own cushion.

35:37.095 --> 35:40.131
- I think Betty's gonna be very
happy with what Gordon did.

35:40.131 --> 35:41.541
I think she's gonna love the fact

35:41.541 --> 35:44.381
that she's become an elegant feature.

35:44.381 --> 35:47.462
- So Babe, I want you to come here please

35:47.462 --> 35:48.851
and stand there.

35:50.518 --> 35:52.844
Now relax, turn around,

35:52.844 --> 35:56.687
I want you look at the
eyes of that picture

35:56.687 --> 35:58.623
and move your head from left to right.

35:58.623 --> 36:00.592
(laughing)

36:00.592 --> 36:05.806
And the eyes move the eyes
follow you around the room.

36:05.947 --> 36:07.950
- Oh my God, the eye portrait.

36:07.950 --> 36:10.822
It was really creepy, but I
would try to stay in there,

36:10.822 --> 36:13.330
I might have another room on backup just

36:13.330 --> 36:14.199
