it through the night

36:14.199 --> 36:17.028
but I would definitely give it a try.

36:17.028 --> 36:18.642
- Ready to see another one?

36:18.642 --> 36:20.171
This one you're gonna love,
it's my favourite one.

36:20.171 --> 36:21.040
Let's go.

36:22.449 --> 36:23.317
Up you go.

36:23.317 --> 36:24.186
Oh my God.

36:25.858 --> 36:28.048
- [Gordon] How beautiful is that?

36:28.048 --> 36:29.999
- Wow, oh my God.

36:29.999 --> 36:30.880
- Just gorgeous.

36:30.880 --> 36:33.069
I really feel the changes
are gonna help T.J. and I

36:33.069 --> 36:35.267
get some things back into focus.

36:35.267 --> 36:38.062
My father would definitely
like a lot of the changes,

36:38.062 --> 36:39.771
I wish he was here to see it.

36:39.771 --> 36:42.714
Now you won't believe what
I have downstairs for you,

36:42.714 --> 36:43.582
let's go.

36:46.164 --> 36:47.244
- [Gordon] Coming up,

36:47.244 --> 36:49.625
- I give Babe a surprise
she'll never forget.

36:49.625 --> 36:52.188
Ever had a French kiss?

36:52.188 --> 36:54.534
(laughing)

36:57.288 --> 37:00.317
- [Gordon] I've just shown
the family their new lobby

37:00.317 --> 37:01.716
and the new bedrooms.

37:01.716 --> 37:03.436
- [T.J.] Oh, oh my God.

37:03.436 --> 37:05.558
- [Gordon] Now it's time to
show them the new improvements

37:05.558 --> 37:08.274
to the hotel restaurant.

37:08.274 --> 37:11.348
The inn has been in the Hardisty
family for four generations

37:11.348 --> 37:13.084
- [Karen] Wow.

37:13.084 --> 37:13.952
- [Gordon] So I've come up

37:13.952 --> 37:16.520
with a new menu that reflects
the family's history.

37:16.520 --> 37:19.024
The Curtis House Family Favourites.

37:19.024 --> 37:20.461
- [Karen] Oh my God!

37:20.461 --> 37:23.375
- [Gordon] Let's start off
with grandma Trudy's crab cake,

37:23.375 --> 37:25.229
a hit every single time.

37:25.229 --> 37:28.247
T.J.'s grilled salmon
and corn, Johnny cakes.

37:28.247 --> 37:31.343
Chris's countrified pork
chop dipped in buttermilk,

37:31.343 --> 37:33.824
so with Mac and cheese,
gravy and green beans.

37:33.824 --> 37:35.167
You're only allowed it once a week, mind.

37:35.167 --> 37:36.684
(laughing)

37:36.684 --> 37:39.297
And when you're cooking your family's food

37:39.297 --> 37:41.750
it's gonna be so much more
love, so much more care

37:41.750 --> 37:43.195
to what you're serving.

37:43.195 --> 37:45.194
Now, tuck in and enjoy.

37:49.236 --> 37:51.300
- [T.J.] Oh, that sauce is unbelievable.

37:51.300 --> 37:53.817
- I'm really excited to
show off the new menu.

37:53.817 --> 37:54.870
This is a good one.

37:54.870 --> 37:56.056
Finally, now this is something

37:56.056 --> 37:58.528
I can tell people it's
really, really good.

37:58.528 --> 37:59.659
- [Chris] Everything here is delicious.

37:59.659 --> 38:01.178
Very, very, very good.

38:01.178 --> 38:02.374
- It's like a new ball game

38:02.374 --> 38:04.234
- [Chris] A whole new ball game.

38:04.234 --> 38:05.537
- Just like us.

38:06.845 --> 38:08.509
- [Gordon] Tonight is the relaunch

38:08.509 --> 38:10.465
of the new improved Curtis House.

38:10.465 --> 38:11.370
As the guests arrive

38:11.370 --> 38:13.748
there's a new sense of
warmth and welcome from T.J.

38:13.748 --> 38:14.965
and the staff.

38:16.179 --> 38:18.849
- Welcome to the Curtis
House. How are you?

38:18.849 --> 38:21.248
- I love the new work and I
can't wait for our customers

38:21.248 --> 38:23.305
to come in 'cause I
wanna see their reaction.

38:23.305 --> 38:24.173
- [Female Guest] Wow.

38:24.173 --> 38:25.104
- [Male Guest] We've got
our own little fireplace.

38:25.104 --> 38:27.416
I love how has that nice cosy cottage feel

38:27.416 --> 38:28.738
but yet modern.

38:28.738 --> 38:30.828
- This is definitely gonna
get people in the rooms

38:30.828 --> 38:32.899
and we're proud to send them up there.

38:32.899 --> 38:33.767
- Welcome to the Curtis House.

38:33.767 --> 38:34.636
- Thank you

38:34.636 --> 38:37.868
- Let me take you upstairs to your room.

38:37.868 --> 38:38.797
- This is delicious.

38:38.797 --> 38:41.047
- [Gordon] Down in the
restaurant, Chris is taking charge

38:41.047 --> 38:43.975
and putting in the care he
needs to make his diners happy.

38:43.975 --> 38:45.139
- That's really good.

38:45.139 --> 38:47.202
- Crab cakes need to
go in the oven, please.

38:47.202 --> 38:48.781
It feels very good to have
the Hardisty name on the menu,

38:48.781 --> 38:50.203
you know, it's where I should be.

38:50.203 --> 38:51.907
Definitely him giving
me a little more focus

38:51.907 --> 38:54.416
a little more direction and a
little more immediate pride.

38:54.416 --> 38:56.702
- Yeah and use the spoon to
put that on please, thank you.

38:56.702 --> 38:58.613
- [T.J.] C'mon Chris, we good, we good?

38:58.613 --> 39:00.620
- [Gordon] More
importantly, T.J. and Chris

39:00.620 --> 39:02.810
are working together and communicating.

39:02.810 --> 39:03.679
- It that gone?

39:03.679 --> 39:04.547
- Yes.

39:04.547 --> 39:06.132
- And then we got a clam
and a slider coming?

39:06.132 --> 39:07.001
- Yes.

39:07.001 --> 39:08.370
I think my brother's and my attitude

39:08.370 --> 39:09.692
has changed dramatically.

39:09.692 --> 39:10.707
Plating my clams right now.

39:10.707 --> 39:12.531
- [Chris] Plating now, thank you.

39:12.531 --> 39:14.925
- My brother and I are back
to working very well together.

39:14.925 --> 39:15.918
- [Chris] How are we doing Trudy?

39:15.918 --> 39:17.131
- [Trudy] We're doing fine,

39:17.131 --> 39:19.757
I'm getting all kinds
of compliments again.

39:19.757 --> 39:22.389
- [Chris] Oh baby, you're
alright Ma, you're alright.

39:22.389 --> 39:23.702
It's definitely one of the
most important things to me is

39:23.702 --> 39:28.163
seeing my mother and my
sister and my family happy.

39:28.163 --> 39:30.647
- [Gordon] T.J. and Chris
are finally working together

39:30.647 --> 39:33.561
but I have one last thing I need to do

39:33.561 --> 39:35.070
to help turn this business around.

39:35.070 --> 39:36.238
You must be Donna, good to see you.

39:36.238 --> 39:37.281
- Thank you.

39:38.232 --> 39:39.838
- I've asked a paranormal expert

39:39.838 --> 39:44.209
to investigate the
spirits haunting the inn.

39:44.209 --> 39:45.599
- Somebody here?

39:48.822 --> 39:51.342
Camera's acting really funky.

39:53.223 --> 39:56.237
- Boo! (laughing)

39:56.237 --> 39:58.062
- You are officially...

39:59.735 --> 40:03.215
a member of the Haunted Connecticut Tours

40:03.215 --> 40:06.085
and you are now officially haunted.

40:06.085 --> 40:06.981
Congratulations, my darling.

40:06.981 --> 40:08.465
- Thank you, thank you very much.

40:08.465 --> 40:09.654
- Hang that up with pride.

40:09.654 --> 40:11.931
Now that the Curtis House
has certified as haunted

40:11.931 --> 40:14.748
and on the ghost tour, it will
attract even more business

40:14.748 --> 40:17.962
and help this family get out of debt.

40:18.899 --> 40:21.457
Ladies, I'm gonna say goodbye.

40:21.457 --> 40:23.313
- No, but we're not
ready for you to leave.

40:23.313 --> 40:24.727
- No, you just can't leave.

40:24.727 --> 40:25.912
- I know my job is done.

40:25.912 --> 40:27.355
You two have been amazing.

40:27.355 --> 40:30.575
If they stop talking to
each other, call me, please.

40:30.575 --> 40:31.538
- I'm gonna miss you.

40:31.538 --> 40:36.114
- Oh no, c'mon Babe. I'm gonna
miss you too. Little kiss?

40:36.114 --> 40:39.851
(mwah) and (mwah) two. You know
they give you four in Paris?

40:39.851 --> 40:41.654
- (laughing) Yes.

40:41.654 --> 40:43.713
- Have you had a French kiss?

40:43.713 --> 40:46.942
- (laughing) Uh oh!

40:46.942 --> 40:48.119
- Just asking (laughing)

40:48.119 --> 40:50.574
- Gordon did give me
two kisses on my cheek.

40:50.574 --> 40:55.788
Yes, I haven't watched it yet (giggling).

40:56.329 --> 40:59.611
- Okay, my time is done,
I'm gonna leave you.

40:59.611 --> 41:00.796
- Appreciate it, thank you very much.

41:00.796 --> 41:04.918
- Yeah, don't let 60 years
of hard work disappear.

41:04.918 --> 41:05.905
- Absolutely not.

41:05.905 --> 41:09.093
- Promise me you're gonna
continue talking to your sister,

41:09.093 --> 41:12.299
the minute you don't, the place is doomed.

41:12.299 --> 41:14.290
And you have a beautiful,
beautiful inn here.

41:14.290 --> 41:15.182
- Thank you very much.

41:15.182 --> 41:17.615
- I can't wait to come back.

41:19.594 --> 41:21.522
Look after yourself, please.

41:21.522 --> 41:22.813
- Thank you.

41:22.813 --> 41:25.586
Gordon Ramsey, put some life back into us.

41:25.586 --> 41:27.455
- Goodnight Betty. Wow.

41:27.455 --> 41:30.119
- Gordon showed us where
our relationship should be

41:30.119 --> 41:31.892
and will be from this point on.

41:31.892 --> 41:33.768
I'm forever grateful to Gordon Ramsey

41:33.768 --> 41:36.943
for coming in here and
straightening us out.

41:36.943 --> 41:41.896
- I ain't afraid of no ghost. (laughing)

41:48.228 --> 41:50.344
- Since my visit T.J.
and Chris have learned

41:50.344 --> 41:52.607
how important it is to work together.

41:52.607 --> 41:55.629
- Hot roasted chicken, mashed
only, turkey as it comes.

41:55.629 --> 41:57.141
Gordon pulled off something
that I wasn't sure

41:57.141 --> 41:58.854
was going to be able to be mended.

41:58.854 --> 42:00.051
I think I got my best friend back

42:00.051 --> 42:02.446
and he's not going anywhere this time.

42:02.446 --> 42:03.314
- There you go.

42:03.314 --> 42:05.008
It was definitely an
eye opening experience,

42:05.008 --> 42:07.242
it's not a daily grind now.

42:07.242 --> 42:08.744
- [Gordon] Bookings for the hotel are up.

42:08.744 --> 42:11.623
- [Donna] If there's any
spirits present in this room.

42:11.623 --> 42:13.299
- [Gordon] And it's bringing in tourists

42:13.299 --> 42:15.427
who want to get a glimpse
of Betty, the ghost.

42:15.427 --> 42:17.740
- Good evening, welcome
to the Curtis House.

42:17.740 --> 42:18.644
If Gordon didn't come

42:18.644 --> 42:21.239
I think we were pretty much done.

42:21.239 --> 42:23.033
You saved my family and

42:23.033 --> 42:26.509
it feels like he gave us our life back.
